{"tid":2212160,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"日日都唔想返工,返工返到唔開心,究竟為左啲乜","createTime":"2020-09-21T14:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T04:48:59.000Z","uid":297561,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4ceffe175ab56361d8e99532c2ba0acff09086da","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"返工返到個人好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返工返到咁辛苦究竟為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉,仲有幾十年工要返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦幾十年就係為左退休有安穩生活,做人有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dae5818df972ed0350cf566a9319e04ece50dc7","tid":2212160,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"你唔返工邊個畀錢我使?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6289265bd4093d42cb34a69fb54534135052c547","tid":2212160,"uid":377671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"思索左呢個問題好耐<br />\n為咗乜要返工<br />\n為咗錢<br />\n咁要錢嚟做乜<br />\n為咗生存<br />\n<br />\n咁點解要為生存而返工"},{"pid":"4f1e08975f95d08543011fa4f08eb37c202cc4a0","tid":2212160,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"我都成日問自己, 就係為咗份人工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a093c4746e879730d1f17a1d6e77dc3fbb27bf","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dae5818df972ed0350cf566a9319e04ece50dc7","tid":2212160,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"你唔返工邊個畀錢我使?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"返左工都唔比錢你洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31a8b0fd0c0116632675b6eb02843e7c0a160bc","tid":2212160