":3,"quote":{"pid":"66279dbb6d35d0583c3e4de451d594b5ce002d91","tid":2212160,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"我返工幾開心<br />\n就係人工低唔開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"好事黎,起碼可以開心先<br />\n好過日日年初四咁既樣返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b48532fa6090b6f19b82f9bab19a9ccc312dab","tid":2212160,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:51:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=05e6830c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5d282c2ea59bfc9318809167d732813fe2382aaf","tid":2212160,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc579bfe9b4c5e8b28d2c4dac8d2f2805b1781b","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31a8b0fd0c0116632675b6eb02843e7c0a160bc","tid":2212160,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"Daddy有錢係生活<br />\n<br />\n老豆窮西係生存<br />\n<br />\n冷靜d望下你爸爸先<br />\n<br />\n接受現實慢慢捱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"捱左好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"四份一時間都未過完"},{"pid":"f37d1847a55e884d728415caedb1ea8bfa82c463","tid":2212160,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7063412dbe97806c3fea602d5b4bb3c698b82afb","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6289265bd4093d42cb34a69fb54534135052c547","tid":2212160,"uid":377671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"思索左呢個問題好耐<br />\n為咗乜要返工<br />\n為咗錢<br />\n咁要錢嚟做乜<br />\n為咗生存<br />\n<br />\n咁點解要為生存而返工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"最好笑既係辛苦幾十年就係為退休生活<br />\n<br />\n篇失業潮文真係講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"05eb3ac78e52b1496293a2c130d44b64af1e9c80","tid":2212160,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6289265bd4093d42cb34a69fb54534135052c547","tid":2212160,"uid":377671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"思索左呢個問題好耐<br />\n為咗乜要返工<br />\n為咗錢<br />\n咁要錢嚟做乜<br />\n為咗生存<br />\n<br />\n咁點解要為生存而返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"唔生存咪唔洗再返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔洗受苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4578e6ed2acf3ce6ef09913112c6ed2503b02c","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"又要訓教聽日又要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2388cf38855242293a26da6e5a016ce61a6a08a3","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37d1847a55e884d728415caedb1ea8bfa82c463","tid":2212160,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7063412dbe97806c3fea602d5b4bb3c698b82afb","tid":2212160,"uid":297561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6289265bd4093d42cb34a69fb54534135052c547","tid":2212160,"uid":377671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"思索左呢個問題好耐<br />\n為咗乜要返工<br />\n為咗錢<br />\n咁要錢嚟做乜<br />\n為咗生存<br />\n<br />\n咁點解要為生存而返工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"最好笑既係辛苦幾十年就係為退休生活<br />\n<br />\n篇失業潮文真係講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣